AxonOS BCI Gateway
==================

This repository is an integration fork of OpenBCI_GUI maintained by AxonOS-org
for hardware-in-the-loop EEG acquisition and AxonOS pipeline testing.

Upstream attribution
--------------------

Original work: OpenBCI_GUI v6.0.0-beta.1

Upstream project: https://github.com/OpenBCI/OpenBCI_GUI

Original author: Joel Murphy and OpenBCI contributors

Original license: MIT

All signal acquisition, hardware communication, GUI behavior, and BrainFlow
integration remain upstream OpenBCI work.

AxonOS modifications
--------------------

AxonOS-side modifications are limited to integration touchpoints:

- LSL stream identifier convention: `axonos-gateway`;
- OSC base namespace convention: `/axonos`;
- AxonOS documentation pointers;
- reference-hardware compatibility notes;
- attribution and fork-maintenance metadata;
- CI checks that verify the fork contract.

The AxonOS modifications are licensed under the same MIT License as the upstream
work.

